{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ETrz62g6ezDnvdK9nBVSXU","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package evolution\n     2→\n     3→import (\n     4→\t\"context\"\n     5→\n     6→\t\"github.com/cloche-dev/cloche/internal/domain\"\n     7→)\n     8→\n     9→// LLMClient abstracts LLM calls for evolution stages.\n    10→type LLMClient interface {\n    11→\tComplete(ctx context.Context, systemPrompt, userPrompt string) (string, error)\n    12→}\n    13→\n    14→// CollectedData is the input to the Classifier and Reflector.\n    15→type CollectedData struct {\n    16→\tRuns            []*domain.Run\n    17→\tCaptures        map[string][]*domain.StepExecution // run_id -> step executions\n    18→\tKnowledgeBase   string                             // contents of knowledge/<workflow>.jsonl\n    19→\tCurrentPrompts  map[string]string                  // relative path -> content\n    20→\tCurrentWorkflow string                             // .cloche file content\n    21→\tWorkflowPath    string                             // path to .cloche file\n    22→\tProjectDir      string\n    23→\tWorkflowName    string\n    24→}\n    25→\n    26→// Lesson is a structured insight extracted by the Reflector.\n    27→type Lesson struct {\n    28→\tID              string   `json:\"id\"`\n    29→\tCategory        string   `json:\"category\"`\n    30→\tStepType        string   `json:\"step_type,omitempty\"`\n    31→\tTarget          string   `json:\"target,omitempty\"`\n    32→\tInsight         string   `json:\"insight\"`\n    33→\tSuggestedAction string   `json:\"suggested_action\"`\n    34→\tEvidence        []string `json:\"evidence\"`\n    35→\tConfidence      string   `json:\"confidence\"`\n    36→}\n    37→\n    38→// EvolutionResult records what an evolution pass produced.\n    39→type EvolutionResult struct {\n    40→\tID             string   `json:\"id\"`\n    41→\tProjectDir     string   `json:\"project_dir\"`\n    42→\tWorkflowName   string   `json:\"workflow_name\"`\n    43→\tTriggerRunID   string   `json:\"trigger_run_id\"`\n    44→\tTimestamp      string   `json:\"timestamp\"`\n    45→\tClassification string   `json:\"classification\"`\n    46→\tChanges        []Change `json:\"changes\"`\n    47→\tKnowledgeDelta string   `json:\"knowledge_delta\"`\n    48→}\n    49→\n    50→// Change describes a single file modification made by evolution.\n    51→type Change struct {\n    52→\tType     string `json:\"type\"`\n    53→\tFile     string `json:\"file\"`\n    54→\tReason   string `json:\"reason\"`\n    55→\tSnapshot string `json:\"snapshot\"`\n    56→}\n    57→\n    58→// CandidateScore captures the outcome of evaluating a candidate on a single run.\n    59→type CandidateScore struct {\n    60→\tCandidateID string  `json:\"candidate_id\"`\n    61→\tRunID       string  `json:\"run_id\"`\n    62→\tScore       float64 `json:\"score\"`\n    63→\tDetails     string  `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n    64→}\n    65→\n    66→// PopulationConfig controls GEPA-style population-based prompt evolution.\n    67→type PopulationConfig struct {\n    68→\tEnabled          bool `json:\"enabled\"`\n    69→\tMaxCandidates    int  `json:\"max_candidates\"`\n    70→\tMinRunsToPromote int  `json:\"min_runs_to_promote\"`\n    71→}\n    72→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3708bbdb-b358-4fbf-9b32-75fc43c9cfe2","uuid":"0bbdd3d4-5458-4b4c-975e-f2a9316667fa","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:57:35.933Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/internal/evolution/types.go","content":"package evolution\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\n\t\"github.com/cloche-dev/cloche/internal/domain\"\n)\n\n// LLMClient abstracts LLM calls for evolution stages.\ntype LLMClient interface {\n\tComplete(ctx context.Context, systemPrompt, userPrompt string) (string, error)\n}\n\n// CollectedData is the input to the Classifier and Reflector.\ntype CollectedData struct {\n\tRuns            []*domain.Run\n\tCaptures        map[string][]*domain.StepExecution // run_id -> step executions\n\tKnowledgeBase   string                             // contents of knowledge/<workflow>.jsonl\n\tCurrentPrompts  map[string]string                  // relative path -> content\n\tCurrentWorkflow string                             // .cloche file content\n\tWorkflowPath    string                             // path to .cloche file\n\tProjectDir      string\n\tWorkflowName    string\n}\n\n// Lesson is a structured insight extracted by the Reflector.\ntype Lesson struct {\n\tID              string   `json:\"id\"`\n\tCategory        string   `json:\"category\"`\n\tStepType        string   `json:\"step_type,omitempty\"`\n\tTarget          string   `json:\"target,omitempty\"`\n\tInsight         string   `json:\"insight\"`\n\tSuggestedAction string   `json:\"suggested_action\"`\n\tEvidence        []string `json:\"evidence\"`\n\tConfidence      string   `json:\"confidence\"`\n}\n\n// EvolutionResult records what an evolution pass produced.\ntype EvolutionResult struct {\n\tID             string   `json:\"id\"`\n\tProjectDir     string   `json:\"project_dir\"`\n\tWorkflowName   string   `json:\"workflow_name\"`\n\tTriggerRunID   string   `json:\"trigger_run_id\"`\n\tTimestamp      string   `json:\"timestamp\"`\n\tClassification string   `json:\"classification\"`\n\tChanges        []Change `json:\"changes\"`\n\tKnowledgeDelta string   `json:\"knowledge_delta\"`\n}\n\n// Change describes a single file modification made by evolution.\ntype Change struct {\n\tType     string `json:\"type\"`\n\tFile     string `json:\"file\"`\n\tReason   string `json:\"reason\"`\n\tSnapshot string `json:\"snapshot\"`\n}\n\n// CandidateScore captures the outcome of evaluating a candidate on a single run.\ntype CandidateScore struct {\n\tCandidateID string  `json:\"candidate_id\"`\n\tRunID       string  `json:\"run_id\"`\n\tScore       float64 `json:\"score\"`\n\tDetails     string  `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// PopulationConfig controls GEPA-style population-based prompt evolution.\ntype PopulationConfig struct {\n\tEnabled          bool `json:\"enabled\"`\n\tMaxCandidates    int  `json:\"max_candidates\"`\n\tMinRunsToPromote int  `json:\"min_runs_to_promote\"`\n}\n","numLines":72,"startLine":1,"totalLines":72}}}
